<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/572638-is-this-book-going-to-get-better-i-m-on">Is this book going to get better? I&#39;m on page 27, and so far I&#39;d say it&#39;s about 25% funny and 75% pretty stupid. Or do I just not &quot;get&quot; this author?</a>
</div>
