  <span id="freeText11122903358045901113" style="display:none">DNF at 10%<br /><br />Another failed speed date with the ebooks I bought a long time ago. The author has a very particular sense of humor which did not make me smile once. I also tried the audiobook and the author's voice made my ears bleed (figuratively). My advice is try a sample before buying this book. You either like it or it makes want to run way. </span>
