              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1384775575720112740">Hilarious and heartfelt. More serious than her first book, but still incredibly genuine and never lacking her sardonic wit. If you are looking for a touching and uproariously funny memoir about what it means to be a human, you&apos;ve found it in this book. </span>
  <span id="freeText1384775575720112740" style="display:none">Hilarious and heartfelt. More serious than her first book, but still incredibly genuine and never lacking her sardonic wit. If you are looking for a touching and uproariously funny memoir about what it means to be a human, you've found it in this book. </span>
